      "text": [
        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنْ وَجَدَ بَرْدَ حُبِّنَا عَلَى قَلْبِهِ فَلْيُكْثِرِ اَلدُّعَاءَ لِأُمِّهِ فَإِنَّهَا لَمْ تَخُنْ أَبَاهُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4745 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said: \"Whoever feels the coolness of our (Ahlulbayt (as)) love in his heart should frequently pray for his mother, for she did not betray his father.\""
        ]
      }
    },
